1
00:00:12,400 --> 00:00:15,667
<i>How about you, Mark?
Did you love me?</i>

2
00:00:15,800 --> 00:00:19,533
<i>What we need to learn now
is how to bounce back.</i>

3
00:00:19,667 --> 00:00:21,533
<i>Why don't you just go back
to the Philippines?</i>

4
00:00:21,667 --> 00:00:22,400
<i> This is a hold-up!</i>

5
00:00:22,533 --> 00:00:23,400
<i> Miss, are you okay?</i>

6
00:00:23,533 --> 00:00:24,900
<i>- I'm okay.
- Are you hurt?</i>

7
00:00:25,033 --> 00:00:26,200
<i>- Gina?
- Gerald?</i>

8
00:00:26,333 --> 00:00:29,200
<i>I'm so happy that you and Gerald
are still going strong.</i>

9
00:00:29,333 --> 00:00:31,167
<i>Who would ever think
that we would last?</i>

10
00:00:31,300 --> 00:00:33,533
<i>It seems that she still
has a bad feeling towards me.</i>

11
00:00:33,700 --> 00:00:36,267
<i>I was happy when
I saw Betsy again.</i>

12
00:00:36,400 --> 00:00:37,567
<i> Did you take my money here?</i>

13
00:00:37,700 --> 00:00:38,433
<i> That's my allowance!</i>

14
00:00:38,567 --> 00:00:40,033
<i> Gerald gave it to me!</i>

15
00:00:40,167 --> 00:00:41,800
<i>Well, then why don't ask again?</i>

16
00:00:41,933 --> 00:00:42,767
<i> That's enough, that's enough!</i>

17
00:00:42,900 --> 00:00:46,067
<i> My life is toxic, Gina!</i>

18
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:47,267
<i> Let me go!</i>

19
00:00:49,800 --> 00:00:51,833
<i>I'm really grateful
for what you did.</i>

20
00:00:51,967 --> 00:00:54,033
<i> Hey, I'll charge you for that!</i>

21
00:00:54,167 --> 00:00:56,700
<i>The NLE results will be out
next week.</i>

22
00:00:56,833 --> 00:00:58,767
<i>Gerald will be preparing
a celebration for me.</i>

23
00:00:58,900 --> 00:00:59,767
<i> You're invited.</i>

24
00:01:02,100 --> 00:01:03,867
<i> What's the occasion, Betsy?</i>

25
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:06,933
Graduation or godmother
for the wedding?

26
00:01:07,100 --> 00:01:08,267
Stupid.

27
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:10,500
My boyfriend will be preparing
a celebration for me later.

28
00:01:10,633 --> 00:01:11,267
That's awesome.

29
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:13,800
And my ex-best friend is coming.

30
00:01:13,933 --> 00:01:15,833
That's why we need to have
a good face card.

31
00:01:15,967 --> 00:01:17,433
We need to fight

32
00:01:17,567 --> 00:01:19,367
- You're really a fighter.
- because she's from America.

33
00:01:19,500 --> 00:01:20,733
Did she marry an American?

34
00:01:22,500 --> 00:01:23,067
No.

35
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:24,500
She's a US citizen.

36
00:01:24,633 --> 00:01:25,433
When she was young,

37
00:01:25,567 --> 00:01:27,733
her parents were already
petitioning her.

38
00:01:27,867 --> 00:01:29,667
You know, wait a minute,
I have something to tell you.

39
00:01:29,800 --> 00:01:31,067
Hey, listen.

40
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,500
Listen.

41
00:01:32,633 --> 00:01:35,667
My niece, she went
to the US immediately

42
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:38,567
because she married her friend
who is a US citizen.

43
00:01:38,700 --> 00:01:40,367
And now, they're going
to get a divorce

44
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:42,500
because she's already a citizen.

45
00:01:42,667 --> 00:01:44,233
Hey, friend, there's a fee.

46
00:01:44,367 --> 00:01:48,433
My acquaintance paid
20,000 to marry a Filipino

47
00:01:48,567 --> 00:01:50,633
who is a US citizen.

48
00:01:50,767 --> 00:01:52,433
Only 20,000?

49
00:01:52,567 --> 00:01:55,167
Friend, dollars.

50
00:01:55,300 --> 00:01:56,433
That's a minimum.

51
00:01:56,567 --> 00:01:57,200
Convert it.

52
00:01:57,333 --> 00:01:58,900
Convert it to pesos, how much?

53
00:02:01,467 --> 00:02:04,300
20,000 US dollars.

54
00:02:04,433 --> 00:02:05,767
Oh my!

55
00:02:05,900 --> 00:02:07,833
- That's huge!
- That's over a million!

56
00:02:07,967 --> 00:02:08,600
Right?

57
00:02:10,333 --> 00:02:16,733
But wait, why would you pay
if you can meet an American?

58
00:02:16,900 --> 00:02:19,900
Because that's what Ronalyn,
the daughter of Ms. Cita, did.

59
00:02:20,033 --> 00:02:21,300
Remember?

60
00:02:21,433 --> 00:02:22,833
She married an American.

61
00:02:22,967 --> 00:02:24,600
Oh, did you see their house now,

62
00:02:24,733 --> 00:02:27,667
