and all her stuff is new.

63
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:30,667
Ronalyn literally hit
the jackpot.

64
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:33,767
Ronalyn, the one with
lots of lice before?

65
00:02:33,900 --> 00:02:34,867
True.

66
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:37,300
Seriously, life is just a matter
of luck, isn't it?

67
00:02:37,433 --> 00:02:40,367
Perfect timing, tomorrow
Ms. Cita is having a party

68
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:43,867
