with him, Betsy.

73
00:02:52,567 --> 00:02:54,233
I don't need an American.

74
00:02:54,367 --> 00:02:56,367
I have a boyfriend, right?

75
00:02:56,500 --> 00:02:59,067
And we can both go to America.

76
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:01,000
- Sure?
- Period.

77
00:03:01,133 --> 00:03:02,667
I hope so.

78
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:04,300
Hey, I have to go.

79
00:03:04,433 --> 00:03:05,833
- Are you done? That's okay?
- Okay, okay.

80
00:03:05,967 --> 00:03:07,367
Okay. You're perfect.

81
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:08,633
Thank you. Bye.

82
00:03:08,767 --> 00:03:09,200
You're beautiful!

83
00:03:09,333 --> 00:03:10,867
Do your best, okay?

84
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,233
Beautiful.

85
00:03:12,367 --> 00:03:13,400
Bye!

86
00:03:54,900 --> 00:03:56,367
Brother, just chill.

87
00:03:56,500 --> 00:03:57,767
You've already eaten two legs.

88
00:03:57,900 --> 00:03:59,000
I'm hungry!

89
00:03:59,133 --> 00:04:00,867
- Why?
- Don't eat the chicken ass,

90
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,000
that's Betsy's favorite.

91
00:04:05,333 --> 00:04:06,867
You know, Son,
I don't understand

92
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,667
why you're making a fuzz me
like this.

93
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:11,433
We're not sure
if Betsy will pass.

94
00:04:11,567 --> 00:04:12,433
I know.

95
00:04:12,567 --> 00:04:14,700
Let's just make a new banner.

96
00:04:14,833 --> 00:04:15,700
Sorry!

97
00:04:15,833 --> 00:04:16,833
We'll make it up next year!

98
00:04:18,033 --> 00:04:20,000
Hey! Stop it!

99
00:04:20,133 --> 00:04:21,033
Mother...

100
00:04:21,167 --> 00:04:22,367
Betsy will pass now.

101
00:04:22,500 --> 00:04:23,367
Just trust me, okay?

102
00:04:23,500 --> 00:04:24,300
Okay.

103
00:04:26,567 --> 00:04:28,500
Gerald!

104
00:04:28,667 --> 00:04:30,200
Oh my God!

105
00:04:30,333 --> 00:04:32,567
I'm touched.

106
00:04:32,700 --> 00:04:35,033
Thank you, Babe!

107
00:04:35,167 --> 00:04:36,433
Thank you.

108
00:04:36,567 --> 00:04:37,400
Love you.

109
00:04:37,533 --> 00:04:38,633
Well, this is it.

110
00:04:38,767 --> 00:04:39,567
I can already feel that

111
00:04:39,700 --> 00:04:42,000
I'm going to be
a registered nurse!

112
00:04:42,133 --> 00:04:43,567
- Sure!
- This is it!

113
00:04:43,700 --> 00:04:44,400
This is it.

114
00:04:48,167 --> 00:04:49,700
So much food.

115
00:04:49,833 --> 00:04:51,433
Gina!

116
00:04:51,567 --> 00:04:53,200
Hi, Gina.

117
00:04:53,333 --> 00:04:54,567
Hello.

118
00:04:54,700 --> 00:04:56,000
Good thing you made it.

119
00:04:56,133 --> 00:04:57,400
Let me take that.

120
00:04:57,533 --> 00:04:59,167
We'll put it here.

121
00:04:59,300 --> 00:05:00,333
Mother, it's Gina.

122
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:04,367
Do you remember?

123
00:05:04,500 --> 00:05:05,500
Betsy and I were friends
with her.

124
00:05:05,633 --> 00:05:06,400
Do you remember?

125
00:05:06,533 --> 00:05:08,367
Sure! Gina!

126
00:05:08,500 --> 00:05:09,400
Hello.

127
00:05:09,533 --> 00:05:12,067
Oh, you look even
prettier now.

128
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:13,700
You're so beautiful!

129
00:05:13,833 --> 00:05:15,533
- Wow, such a sweet talker.
- Thank you.

130
00:05:19,033 --> 00:05:21,000
Betsy!

131
00:05:21,133 --> 00:05:22,800
Congratulations!

132
00:05:22,933 --> 00:05:23,900
Hey, hey!

133
00:05:24,033 --> 00:05:25,667
Hey, thank you for the cake!

134
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:27,833
You're so sweet.

135
00:05:27,967 --> 00:05:29,233
Thank you.

136
00:05:29,367 --> 00:05:30,067
Thank you.

137
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:31,200
This is so delicious.

138
00:05:31,333 --> 00:05:32,900
She's beautiful and kind too,
right, Son?

139
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:36,567
By the way,
the PRC list is here!

140
00:05:36,733 --> 00:05:38,200
- That's why we're celebrating.
- Here it is.

141
00:05:38,333 --> 00:05:39,433
Okay, okay.

142
00:05:39,567 --> 00:05:39,933
Well, come on.

143
00:05:40,067 --> 00:05:42,167
Here it is.

144
00:05:42,300 --> 00:05:43,000
Here it is.

145
00:05:46,267 --> 00:05:48,633
Here it is.

146
00:05:48,767 --> 00:05:51,633
Morales, Zenaida Faraon.

147
00:05:51,767 --> 00:05:56,167
Moralla, Arra Isabella Uy.

148
00:05:56,300 --> 00:05:59,333
Oh, Betsy.

149
00:05:59,467 --> 00:06:01,933
Betsy, Morales,
but your name is still not here.

150
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:07,833
That's what I'm saying.

151
00:06:11,733 --> 00:06:12,967
But this is right.

152
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,667
Betsy.

153
00:06:29,367 --> 00:06:31,767
This is my third take.

154
00:06:31,900 --> 00:06:34,367
I can't take it again.

155
00:06:34,500 --> 00:06:35,067
Nothing.

156
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:36,667
I'm done, Gerald.

157
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:40,633
I am not going to be
a nurse in America.

158
00:06:42,767 --> 00:06:44,500
Why don't we do this?

159
00:06:44,633 --> 00:06:49,167
I'll just take the NCLEX first,
I'll get you when I get there.

160
00:06:49,300 --> 00:06:51,933
