so I could work illegally.

165
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:22,467
Betsy, don't lose hope.

166
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:25,833
There are many other ways
for you to go to the US.

167
00:07:25,967 --> 00:07:28,200
You can get sponsored
by a company.

168
00:07:28,333 --> 00:07:29,467
There are many other ways.

169
00:07:32,367 --> 00:07:34,800
<i>My niece was able to go
to the US.</i>

170
00:07:34,933 --> 00:07:37,500
<i>Because she married
her US citizen friend.</i>

171
00:07:37,633 --> 00:07:39,233
<i>And now, they're going
to get a divorce</i>

172
00:07:39,367 --> 00:07:42,033
<i>because she's already a citizen.</i>

173
00:07:42,167 --> 00:07:44,867
So, what's your plan?

174
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:47,267
Why do you want to know?

175
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:48,567
Can you help us?

176
00:07:53,467 --> 00:07:54,667
No, no, no.

177
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:57,900
