get anything from meeting me.

257
00:11:43,067 --> 00:11:44,900
You'll get more later.

258
00:11:45,033 --> 00:11:46,733
Just wait.

259
00:11:46,867 --> 00:11:48,900
Wow! Ms. Cita,
the rumors are true.

260
00:11:49,033 --> 00:11:50,400
You're already successful!

261
00:11:50,533 --> 00:11:52,233
Seriously, these are delicious.

262
00:11:52,367 --> 00:11:54,233
Of course.

263
00:11:54,367 --> 00:11:55,767
When you go to our house,

264
00:11:55,900 --> 00:11:58,367
